{"tid":748702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高呼「 結束一黨專政」算唔算「危害國家安全」？如果是，請立即取締支聯會。","createTime":"2018-07-19T11:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T14:42:54.000Z","uid":54684,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e33b19cea9fd1e21fa462cd02f7a5940adadbe65","tid":748702,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T11:58:35.000Z","msg":"今年，2月尾三中全會confirm修憲，<br />\n<strong><strong>中國共產黨領導 = 中國制度最根本既特徵</strong></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">攻擊</span>中國共產黨領導 = <span style=\"color: red;\">攻擊</span>中國制度最根本既特徵 。</strong><br />\n<br />\n《中共中央關於修改憲法部分內容的建議》<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/194917_d2990e6aae721ac9bbeac587a78f3513.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F194917_d2990e6aae721ac9bbeac587a78f3513.jpg&h=a199193d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/194436_6f419196818f60dd9e7b436c67f23057.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F194436_6f419196818f60dd9e7b436c67f23057.jpg&h=f3c25998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支聯會每年六四集會︰<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/193749_91ab32a0c3b8f6c29730997d04f0f2b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F193749_91ab32a0c3b8f6c29730997d04f0f2b4.jpg&h=b6d9bb53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1) 高呼「 結束一黨專政」，政擊中國憲法指明既，中國制度最根本既特徵，明顯「危害國家安全」;<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/195147_22bc0647cea91c5a919494fed50dc17c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F195147_22bc0647cea91c5a919494fed50dc17c.png&h=9c838d50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/195151_b74cd89a74c7b79acb3e9ad6606665cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F195151_b74cd89a74c7b79acb3e9ad6606665cb.jpg&h=7ed95213&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2) 場內場外不斷要求大批市民捐錢，每年有大量收入，明顯係實際行動去取得Funding，去追求佢地該個「危害國家安全」既主旨;<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/195039_aa2ad4f71eb817be33116d114eb041c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F195039_aa2ad4f71eb817be33116d114eb041c5.jpg&h=c3687cc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3) 下下都幾萬人，就算用警方數字，最高峰都幾千人，明顯 &gt;1 人，係一個組織，更聚集大量群眾，並share火種，嚴重破壞社會安寧。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/195359_f3d5db8a8def5ac2551eba66319d843f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F195359_f3d5db8a8def5ac2551eba66319d843f.jpg&h=fdedf95f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/195405_5fc5c0850a9f916a957abf75308efa34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F195405_5fc5c0850a9f916a957abf75308efa34.jpg&h=2eabe987&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n保安局局長亦都咁講，所以支聯會必定係一個社團︰<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/194639_1a44ad42c85ba4033b3d9f69ab2e69a8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F194639_1a44ad42c85ba4033b3d9f69ab2e69a8.png&h=8568d8a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4) 同內地民權人士有聯絡，更資助佢地，更於大會上播出片段，明顯 同外地人士有聯繫去「危害國家安全」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/195633_6aec94f664d864605a55e0c8e06cc861.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F195633_6aec94f664d864605a55e0c8e06cc861.jpg&h=fee69ef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基於 (1) + (2) + (3) + (4)，<br />\n支聯會有明確意圖去「危害國家安全」，<br />\n支聯會收錢去「危害國家安全」，<br />\n支聯會聯絡國內外人士去「危害國家安全」，<br />\n<br />\n<strong>由此可以定論，支聯會必須取締。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/19/194712_90e062ec93c4c83586b9fd7d25470d45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F19%2F194712_90e062ec93c4c83586b9fd7d25470d45.jpg&h=a0c18e67&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ba335fbee5c664c6adc9a823b34844fc430cdfe","tid":748702,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}